Pre-Game Insights: Jos Buttler: 'We showed the true version of ourselves. We haven't shown enough what we're capable of.'
Babar Azam: 'We conceded a few too many runs. We bowled a few loose deliveries towards the end.'
David Willey: 'You only have to look around the dressing room; we've got massive talent. There's no doubt we've underperformed here which is disappointing.'
Post-Match Reflections: Jos Buttler: 'We spoke together about how if this is the last game for a lot of players, then let's make some good memories at the very least.'
David Willey: 'People might have frowned at the timing of my retirement but nit many players get to walk out on their own terms.'
Babar Azam: 'We will sit together and take stock. We'll take positives from this and discuss mistakes.'
